beer.beer_description: Spring is the perfect time for a clean-out. We took a look in our coolroom and realised it just so happened we had the odds and ends to make this one-off IPA and latest edition to our Stunt Beer series. It has a punchy hop character from some Aussie Topaz, US Chinook and fresh Simcoe Lupulin powder, and enough of a malt backbone to keep it in check. It packs a bit of a punch at 7.2% ABV. Limited release.
